subtitleNullable: Has set of 14 breeds of dogs each having approximately 50 images
descriptionNullable:
### Context

There are various breeds of dogs which looks similar by human observation but they all have different food requirements and care to be taken for their proper growth.The dataset created  above tends to solve this problem by creating the best classification model which is able to distinguish the dogs amoung 14 breeds of dogs.

### Content

The dataset contains 14 folders with folder name denoting the breed name of the dog and each folder containing approximately 50 images,containing approximately 700 total images .


### Acknowledgements

The dataset has been created  with various utility functions created by me in combination with Azure cognitive services api for image search which yielded in getting datasets with ease.


### Inspiration

Build a dog breed classification model which predicts the dog breed on any test image of the dog.
